{"tid":2159662,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"束の間の一花(束間之花)，兩個將死之人嘅愛情","createTime":"2020-08-16T12:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T08:25:37.000Z","uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b774db141bce2ed8267fe8e60dff11e683e3dfe6","tid":2159662,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X2D8cU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X2D8cU.jpg&h=03374abf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講述身患絕症嘅女主喺大學遇上溫柔嘅講師男主，日日上佢堂，愛上左佢<br />\n<br />\n但一年後男主突然辭職，兩個人再冇見過面，喺日常中度過<br />\n<br />\n某日女主喺地下鐵度再次見翻男主，先發現左男主同樣身患絕症命不久矣<br />\n<br />\n詳細有興趣再自己睇，暫時仲連載中<br />\n<br />\n做嘅嘢同普通戀愛咁拍拖行街食飯，但加埋兩個人嘅背景同對白設計，好有生命無常feel，自殺過嘅朋友睇完會有共嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n誠心推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7e7ea8bacf0ea1cef0b76bc09dbde1f7538227","tid":2159662,"uid":191467,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"你隻賤速又改名"},{"pid":"4da936a08f83a54c93bd5a0bd0f4231cc357ef59","tid":2159662,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2e7e7ea8bacf0ea1cef0b76bc09dbde1f7538227","tid":2159662,"uid":191467,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"你隻賤速又改名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"不要25=="},{"pid":"60c1a249a972b8c1d342b91a294ee59e5642dc32","tid":2159662,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4da936a08f83a54c93bd5a0bd0f4231cc357ef59","tid":2159662,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2e7e7ea8bacf0ea1cef0b76bc09dbde1f7538227","tid":2159662,"uid":191467,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"你隻賤速又改名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"不要25=="},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"你五毛 你PR<img s